iv class="main_menu_list"><h4>Higher Education</h4><div><h5><a href="/education-software">Education Solutions</a></h5><p><a href="/competency-based-education-solution">Competency based education</a>, <a href="/outcome-based-education-software">Outcome based education</a>,<a href="/accreditation-management-software"> Accreditation</a>,<a href="/artificial-intelligence-in-higher-education"> AI</a>,<a href="/chatbot-for-higher-education"> Chatbot</a></p></div><div><h5><a href="/student-lifecycle-management-software">Student Management</a></h5><p><a href="/student-recruitment-software">Recruitment</a>, <a href="/student-admission-system">Admission</a>, <a href="/student-registration-enrollment">Registration &amp; Enrollment</a>, <a href="/fee-management-system">Fee</a>, <a href="/student-information-system">Student Information System</a></p></div><div><h5><a href="/faculty-management-software">Faculty Management</a></h5><p><a href="/classroom-management-system">Classroom</a>, <a href="/attendance-management-system">Attendance</a>, <a href="/leave-management-system">Leave</a>, <a href="/assignment-management-system">Assignment</a>, <a href="/examination-management-system">Examination</a>, <a href="/gradebook-management-software">Gradebook</a>, <a href="/faculty-evaluation-system">Evaluation</a>, <a href="/student-tracking-software">Student Tracking</a>, <a href="/mobile-document-management-system">Documents</a>, <a href="/cms-for-higher-education">Portal CMS</a></p></div><div><h5><a href="/course-evaluation-software">Course Management</a></h5><p><a href="/course-catalog-software">Course Catalog</a>, <a href="/curriculum-management-software">Curriculum</a>, <a href="/timetable-management-system">Timetable</a>, <a href="/syllabus-lesson-planning-software">Syllabus &amp; Lesson Plan</a>, <a href="/report-card-management-system">Report Card</a>, <a href="/student-transcript-management">Transcripts</a></p></div><div><h5><a href="/campus-management-solutions">Campus Management</a></h5><p><a href="/sis-for-higher-education">Student</a>, <a href="/staff-management-software">Staff</a>, <a href="/alumni-management-software">Alumni</a>, <a href="/accounting-financial-management">Finance</a>, <a href="/placement-management-software">Placement</a></p></div><div><h5><a href="/facilities-management-system">Facilities Management</a></h5><p><a href="/college-library-management">Library</a>, <a href="/hostel-management-system">Hostel</a>, <a href="/asset-management-system">Asset</a>, <a href="/college-inventory-management-system">Inventory</a>, <a href="/event-management">Events</a></p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="panel-panel panel-col-last"><div class="inside"><div class="panel-pane pane-block pane-block-125 pane-block" ><div class="pane-content"><div class="main_menu_list"><h4>By Institute Type</h4><div><h5><a href="/higher-education">Universities &amp; Higher Education</a></h5><p>Versatile ERP software for higher education that connects departments &amp; functions.</p></div><div><h5><a href="/engineering-college-management-software">Engineering &amp; Arts Colleges</a></h5><p>Most comprehensive software to manage admission, fees, attendance,etc.</p></div><div><h5>Medical &amp; Dental Colleges</h5><p>Interactive education software for students, faculty &amp; management in all departments.</p></div><div><h5>Community Colleges</h5><p>Complete college automation software to manage academic &amp; admin processes.</p></div><div><h5>Technical Institutes</h5><p>Enroll in online courses &amp; tests and enhance your skills &amp; knowledge.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></li><li class="muchomenu-parent even half-1"><span class="muchomenu-parent-title"><li><a href=aboutus.php>Aboutus</a></li> </span><div class="muchomenu-bin muchomenu-slots muchomenu-bin-3 "><div class="panel-display panel-1col clearfix" ><div class="panel-panel panel-col"><div><div class="panel-pane pane-block pane-block-126 pane-block" ><div class="pane-content"><div class="about_us_submenu"><ul class="sub_menu about_us"><li><a href="/about-us">Overview</a></li><li><a href="/higher-education-blog">Insights</a></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></li><li class="muchomenu-parent odd half-1"><span class="muchomenu-parent-title"><li><a href=login2.php>Login</a></span></li><li class="muchomenu-parent even half-2"><span class="muchomenu-parent-title"><span class="muchomenu-parent-title"><a href="/" class="muchomenu-item muchomenu-item-5 odd last" target="" id="menu-demo">DEMO</a></span></li></ul></div></div></div> </nav></div></div> </header><div class="main-container full-width"> <header role="banner" id="page-header"> </header><div class="main-content"> <section class="full-width"> <a id="main-content"></a><div class="region region-content"><div id="block-block-46" class="block block-block"><div class="content"><div class="nav-box-outer"><div class="navigator-box2"><span class="open-box demo_opt"><span class="vertical-text">Demo </span> <i class="fa fa-chevron-left">&nbsp;</i> <i class="fa fa-chevron-right">&nbsp;</i> </span><div class="nav-box-inner"><ul class="feature-list2-scroll"><li><i class="fa fa-desktop">&nbsp;</i> <a class="colorbox-load" href="/request_demo" id="block-system-mainBtn" oncontextmenu="return false" rel="lightframe">Request a Demo</a></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div><div id="block-system-main" class="block block-system"><div class="content"><div class="bootstrap-twocol-stacked" ><div class="row-fluid"><div class="panel-pane pane-block pane-block-85 pane-block sis_banner" ><div class="pane-content"><div class="section-content tab-section parallax" data-stellar-background-ratio="0.6"><div class="tab-box sis_school"><div class="container">
triggerAnimation animated"><div class="tab-pane active" id="trendy"><div class="left_first"><h1>Leave Management System</h1><p>Creatrix Campus leave management system offers a wide range of features and functionality, which lets educational institutions of every size to know that all their students and staff leave requests are managed efficiently</p></div><div class="row left_row"><div class="col-md-4"><ul class="cms_list school_list triggerAnimation animated" data-animate="slideInLeft"><li><div><span class="mgmt_title"><i class="fa fa-cog">&nbsp;</i></span><h3>Easy setup &amp; user-friendly</h3><p>Time &amp; leave management system is simple, easy to use, and fully customizable; Centrally store all data in one place.</p></div></li><li><div><span class="mgmt_title"><i class="fa fa-tasks">&nbsp;</i></span><h3>Mobile leave management system</h3><p>Using college management software access absence and leave data of students &amp; staff from anywhere, anytime on iPhone &amp; Android devices.</p></div></li></ul></div></div><div class="row right_row"><div class="col-md-4"><ul class="cms_list school_list triggerAnimation animated" data-animate="slideInLeft"><li><div><span class="mgmt_title"><i class="fa fa-desktop">&nbsp;</i></span><h3>Organize and monitor leave data</h3><p>High level of data security and integrity. Complete audit trails of leave requests using absence management software in higher education.</p></div></li><li><div><span class="mgmt_title"><i class="fa fa-group">&nbsp;</i></span><h3>Multi-level leave approval</h3><p>Improved visibility to leaves and absences of students and staff; Approve, reject or cancel time-off leave requests using online leave management system.</p></div></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="row-fluid"><div class="panel-pane pane-block pane-block-87 pane-block sis_styles cms_styles" ><div class="pane-content"><div class="shortcodes-elem container"><h1>Features</h1><div class="row"><div class="col-md-4"><div class="separator"><ul class="feature-list2"><li><span><i class="fa fa-cloud">&nbsp;</i></span><div class="list-cont"><h3>Cloud Services</h3><p>Manage the leave records of your institution using cloud-based school management software. Users can securely access leave information over the web or mobile devices. We take care of customizations, upgrades, storage, data backups, and maintenance.</p></div></li></ul></div><div class="separator"><ul class="feature-list2"><li><span><i class="fa fa-group">&nbsp;</i></span><div class="list-cont"><h3>Track Leave Requests</h3><p>Automated leave management process right from the initial request from students or parents. Teachers can track leave requests of students from website and mobile devices.</p></div></li></ul></div><div class="separator"><ul class="feature-list2"><li><span><i class="fa fa-th-list">&nbsp;</i></span><div class="list-cont"><h3>Customizable Leave Reporting</h3><p>Built-in reporting tools helps the administrator to create a wide range of leave reports, forms and letters using leave records. Track leave patterns and trends on the dashboard in real-time using charts.</p></div></li></ul></div><ul class="feature-list2"></ul></div><div class="col-md-4"><div class="separator"><ul class="feature-list2"><li><span><i class="fa fa-user">&nbsp;</i></span><div class="list-cont"><h3>Employee Leave Management</h3><p>Using employee leave management system employees can apply leaves easily. HR can track and record all types of leave and absence of employees, with the ability to approve or reject leave, and maintain leave account accurately and efficiently.</p></div></li></ul></div><div class="separator"><ul class="feature-list2"><li><span><i class="fa fa-edit">&nbsp;</i></span><div class="list-cont"><h3>Add/Edit Leave Types</h3><p>The administrator can add/edit different types of leave. Customize leave types and configure leave policies for any type of institution having campuses in multiple locations.</p></div></li></ul></div><div class="separator"><ul class="feature-list2"><li><span><i class="fa fa-calendar">&nbsp;</i></span><div class="list-cont"><h3>Calendar Integration</h3><p>Administrator can set up the specific calendar type or integrate Google Calendar. Display rest days, holidays and leave in the calendar. Plan and manage leave and absences of students and staff to ensure smooth functioning of the institution.</p></div></li></ul></div><ul class="feature-list2"></ul></div><div class="col-md-4"><div class="separator"><ul class="feature-list2"><li><span><i class="fa fa-calendar">&nbsp;</i></span><div class="list-cont"><h3>Holidays &amp; Events Scheduler</h3><p>Online academic scheduling system helps you to easily plan and schedule holidays and events during the academic year via web, iOS &amp; Android devices. Send automatic notifications on important events to students, staff, teachers, parents and alumni by Email and SMS.</p></div></li></ul></div><div class="separator"><ul class="feature-list2"><li><span><i class="fa fa-envelope">&nbsp;</i></span><div class="list-cont"><h3>Notifications &amp; Reminders</h3><p>Notify leave and absences of students or staff via email, SMS, and messaging. Send alerts on important events and news updates on various channels at once to the selected contacts.</p></div></li></ul></div><div class="separator"><ul class="feature-list2"><li><span><i class="fa fa-edit">&nbsp;</i></span><div class="list-cont"><h3>Approve Leave Requests</h3><p>Online leave management system for schools allows you to automatically assign leave requests to the school authorities for final approval. Users can check their leave balance and history in the higher education leave management module.</p></div></li></ul></div><ul class="feature-list2"></ul></div></div></div></div></div><div class="panel-separator"></div><div class="panel-pane pane-block pane-block-86 pane-block sis_styles cms_styles_benefits attendance_style" ><div class="pane-content"><div class="shortcodes-elem container"><h1>Benefits</h1><div class="row"><div class="col-md-4"><div class="separator"><ul class="feature-list2"><li><span><i class="fa fa-map-marker">&nbsp;</i></span><div class="list-cont management-list"><h3>Streamline Leave Process</h3><em><i class="fa fa-angle-right">&nbsp;</i></em><p>Eliminate manual work and streamline leave process</p><em><i class="fa fa-angle-right">&nbsp;</i></em><p>Standardize leave types and set up complex leave policies</p><em><i class="fa fa-angle-right">&nbsp;</i></em><p>In-built database to manage leave with automatic backup for safety and reliability</p><em><i class="fa fa-angle-right">&nbsp;</i></em><p>Complete automation of leave management process.</p></div></li></ul></div></div><div class="col-md-4"><div class="separator"><ul class="feature-list2"><li><span><i class="fa fa-file">&nbsp;</i></span><div class="list-cont management-list"><h3>Efficient Leave Administration</h3><em><i class="fa fa-angle-right">&nbsp;</i></em><p>Track leave and absences of students and staff with precision</p><em><i class="fa fa-angle-right">&nbsp;</i></em><p>Clear, consistent and fact-based guidance to approve leave requests</p><em><i class="fa fa-angle-right">&nbsp;</i></em><p>Automatic update of leave information ensures effective tracking of absences</p><em><i class="fa fa-angle-right">&nbsp;</i></em><p>Reduce unexcused absences, overhead expenses and manage leave intelligently</p></div></li></ul></div></div><div class="col-md-4"><div class="separator"><ul class="feature-list2"><li><span><i class="fa fa-map-marker">&nbsp;</i></span><div class="list-cont management-list"><h3>Resource Optimization</h3><em><i class="fa fa-angle-right">&nbsp;</i></em><p>Simplify leave management, reduce staff workload and improve efficiency</p><em><i class="fa fa-angle-right">&nbsp;</i></em><p>Easy to plan leave to ensure that departments are adequately staffed</p><em><i class="fa fa-angle-right">&nbsp;</i></em><p>Graphical analysis of leave links the performance of students and staff</p><em><i class="fa fa-angle-right">&nbsp;</i></em><p>Cloud services ensure time and cost savings as well as increased productivity</p></div></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="row-fluid"></div></div></div></div></div> </section></div><div class="section-content content-bottom"><div class="region region-content-bottom"><div id="block-addthis-addthis-block" class="block block-addthis"><div class="content"></div></div></div></div></div> <footer class="full-width"><div><div class="region region-pre-footer"><div id="block-block-5" class="block block-block"><div class="content"><div class="social-section"><ul class="social-icons triggerAnimation animated" data-animate="fadeIn"><li><a class="facebook" href="https://www.facebook.com/CreatrixCampus" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-facebook">&nbsp;</i></a></li><li><a class="twitter" href="https://twitter.com/creatrixcampus" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-twitter">&nbsp;</i></a></li><li><a class="google" href="https://plus.google.com/u/0/106978292400587788479/posts" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-google-plus">&nbsp;</i></a></li><li><a class="linkedin" href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/creatrix-campus" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-linkedin">&nbsp;</i></a></li><li><a class="pinterest" href="http://www.pinterest.com/creatrixcampus" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-pinterest">&nbsp;</i></a></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div><div class="up-footer"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="region region-footer"><div id="block-block-7" class="block block-block col-md-3"><div class="content"><div class="widget footer-widget text-widget"><h1>About</h1><p>Creatrix Campus is just not another run-of-the-mill campus management system.</p><p>Creatrix Campus has been built by a team of passionate folks and has tons of features that will help you help your students because as the saying goes â€“ A Good education is the greatest GIFT you can give to anyone!</p><a href="